nodes.text: "Black-Eye" Cahoon was a male Clantaani criminal who was an associate of the Tatooine gang leader Longo Two-Guns. During his time on Tatooine, he was believed to have played a role in the kidnapping of some of Jabba the Hutt's Twi'lek dancing girls. As a result, he was captured by Jango Fett who claimed the bounty from Jabba.
The bounty is 5,000 credits alive and 2,500 credits dead. It is up to the players decision on which way.
